{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:13:59 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:13:59 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">Tibetan verbs fall into two main classes: <strong>volitional verbs</strong> and <strong>non-volitional verbs</strong>. The grammar of European languages does not make this opposition between volitional and non-volitional. However, in terms of vocabulary the differentiation can be observed. For example, &ldquo;hear&rdquo; and &ldquo;see&rdquo; are non-volitional, while &ldquo;listen&rdquo; and &ldquo;look&rdquo; are volitional.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Within each of these two main classes, a distinction is made between <strong>transitive verbs </strong>and <strong>intransitive verbs</strong>. Transitive verbs require an object, whereas intransitive verbs do not.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">There are, then, altogether four basic classes of verbs: non-volitional intransitive, volitional intransitive, non-volitional transitive, and volitional transitive.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Table: Examples of the Four Verb Classes</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Volitional</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་རང་དབང་ཅན་<em>&nbsp;</em></span><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Non-Volitional</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་གཞན་དབང་ཅན་<em>&nbsp;</em></span><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Transitive</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་ཐ་དད་པ་</span></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྟ</span>་   &ldquo;Look&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉན</span>་   &ldquo;Listen&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཟོ་</span> &ldquo;Make&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མཐོང</span>་   &ldquo;See&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གོ་</span> &ldquo;Hear&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཧ་ག</span>ོ་   &ldquo;Understand&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Intransitive</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་ཐ་མི་དད་པ་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉལ་</span> &ldquo;Lie down&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལང་</span> &ldquo;Get up&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགྲོ་</span> &ldquo;Go&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"192\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ན</span>་   &ldquo;Be sick&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཤི་</span> &ldquo;Die&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲག་</span> &ldquo;Recover&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Volitional</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་རང་དབང་ཅན་<em>&nbsp;</em></span><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Non-Volitional</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་གཞན་དབང་ཅན་<em>&nbsp;</em></span><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Transitive</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་ཐ་དད་པ་</span></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྟ</span>་   &ldquo;Look&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉན</span>་   &ldquo;Listen&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཟོ་</span> &ldquo;Make&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མཐོང</span>་   &ldquo;See&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གོ་</span> &ldquo;Hear&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཧ་ག</span>ོ་   &ldquo;Understand&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Intransitive</em></p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་ཐ་མི་དད་པ་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉལ་</span> &ldquo;Lie down&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལང་</span> &ldquo;Get up&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགྲོ་</span> &ldquo;Go&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ན</span>་   &ldquo;Be sick&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཤི་</span> &ldquo;Die&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲག་</span> &ldquo;Recover&rdquo;</p>\n","title":""}]}